So, Saturday night--
time to cut loose, right?

05:53.833 --> 05:55.633
Who wants to split a beer?

05:55.635 --> 05:57.335
Oh, we're not drinking here.

05:57.337 --> 05:58.970
Tonight we're going big.

05:58.972 --> 06:01.606
Let's see, what club
should we hit first?

06:01.608 --> 06:04.242
There's Club Was,
there's Wrong...

06:04.244 --> 06:06.578
Um, those places shut
down a long time ago.

06:06.580 --> 06:07.245
Oh, no.

06:07.247 --> 06:08.279
Oh, No shut down, too.

06:08.281 --> 06:09.881
There's Where?
Where's Where?

06:09.883 --> 06:11.349
Where's where Was
was, isn't it?

06:11.351 --> 06:14.119
No, Was wasn't where Where was,
Was was where Wrong was, right?

06:14.121 --> 06:16.221
Okay. Not Okay.
That place is lame.

06:16.223 --> 06:18.723
Okay is Lame?
I thought Lame was a gay bar.

06:18.725 --> 06:19.758
Or is that Wrong?

06:19.760 --> 06:21.626
That's wrong.
That's not Wrong.

06:21.628 --> 06:22.560
Guys, focus.

06:22.562 --> 06:24.028
Oh, I like Focus.
Let's go there.

06:24.030 --> 06:25.730
Where?
Not Where. Focus.

06:25.732 --> 06:27.232
I thought Focus
was closed.

06:27.234 --> 06:28.400
No, Was was Closed.

06:28.402 --> 06:30.835
Once Was shut down,
it reopened as Closed.

06:30.837 --> 06:31.870
So Closed is open.

06:31.872 --> 06:32.771
No, Closed is closed.

06:32.773 --> 06:33.772
I don't know.

06:33.774 --> 06:35.540
Third base! Right?

06:35.542 --> 06:37.375
Ew, Third Base
is all frat guys.

06:37.377 --> 06:38.543
I'll go anyplace, okay?

06:38.545 --> 06:40.578
Not Okay. Okay is lame.

06:40.580 --> 06:41.730
Okay is not Lame.

06:41.732 --> 06:43.214
Lame is a gay bar.

06:43.216 --> 06:44.115
Guys, shut up.

06:44.117 --> 06:45.450
No, Shut up shut down.

06:45.452 --> 06:48.319
I can't believe I don't
know the clubs anymore.

06:48.321 --> 06:50.422
Guys, just pick
a club, okay?

06:50.424 --> 06:52.023
Not Okay!

06:52.025 --> 06:53.291
Okay is Lame!

06:53.293 --> 06:55.493
Gay bar.

06:55.495 --> 06:58.730
For the record, I was in
there once by accident.

06:58.732 --> 07:01.633
I'm pretty sure it's
pronounced Lamé.

07:01.635 --> 07:04.536
It's hopeless, isn't it?

07:04.538 --> 07:06.904
<i>Wow.</i>

07:06.906 --> 07:08.840
A lot of these girls
are young enough

07:08.842 --> 07:10.408
to be our daughters.
I know.

07:10.410 --> 07:12.076
Daddy's home.

07:12.078 --> 07:14.245
And Granddaddy's home!

07:15.047 --> 07:16.815
Tonight rocks so hard!

07:16.817 --> 07:19.384
I might be allergic
to this stamp.

07:23.689 --> 07:25.857
Oh, my God,
my secret crush is here.

07:25.859 --> 07:26.825
Mila Kunis?!

07:26.827 --> 07:29.594
No, <i>my</i> secret crush.

07:29.596 --> 07:32.397
We met a few
years ago.

07:34.467 --> 07:37.302
Hi. I could use
a woman's opinion.

07:37.304 --> 07:40.004
Is this working for me?

07:40.006 --> 07:41.639
Uh... no.

07:42.576 --> 07:43.625
The only good thing

07:43.627 --> 07:45.109
about how ugly that shirt is,

07:45.111 --> 07:48.847
is that it distracts
from how terribly it fits you.

07:48.849 --> 07:50.915
I was trying on the pants.

07:50.917 --> 07:52.917
Oh.

07:53.652 --> 07:55.170
I had to leave
before we could

07:55.172 --> 07:56.521
finish talking,
so that was it.

07:56.523 --> 07:57.722
You know, ever
since then, I've...

07:57.724 --> 07:59.991
Oh, my God, he's
coming over here.

07:59.993 --> 08:01.259
Oh. Hello.

08:01.261 --> 08:03.695
Hi. A few years ago at a
department store, Hi.

08:03.697 --> 08:05.597
did you embarrass
the hell out of me?

08:05.599 --> 08:08.266
Oh, I'm sorry,
you must have me confused

08:08.268 --> 08:11.436
with the shirt
you were wearing that day.

08:11.438 --> 08:13.137
I should be so lucky.

08:13.139 --> 08:14.906
Hi! I'm Ted!

08:14.908 --> 08:16.524
Robin's boyfriend!

08:16.526 --> 08:17.842
Nice to meet you.

08:17.844 --> 08:19.310
Right.

08:19.312 --> 08:21.746
Um... it was really nice
to see you again.

08:21.748 --> 08:23.615
Mm-hmm. You, too.
Yeah.

08:24.618 --> 08:26.868
You owe me one.

08:28.120 --> 08:29.554
Man, isn't this
place great?

08:29.556 --> 08:32.157
Uh, I don't know.
It's so loud!

08:32.159 --> 08:33.491
And so bourgeois.

08:33.493 --> 08:36.628
Many of plays are
about the bourgeois.

08:37.328 --> 08:38.395
And ennui.

08:39.198 --> 08:42.500
And one rock opera about...

08:42.501 --> 08:44.903
a frozen yogurt shop.

08:46.839 --> 08:49.674
Uh, L-Lily, uh, talk
about your open marriage.

08:49.676 --> 08:53.478
Okay. Well, after a long day
of style meetings

08:53.480 --> 08:55.180
and photo shoots

08:55.182 --> 08:56.447
and being
way too mean

08:56.449 --> 08:57.565
to my assistant,

08:57.567 --> 09:00.552
I sometimes bang
an underwear model.

09:00.554 --> 09:01.419
My goodness!

09:01.421 --> 09:02.554
I sleep around, too.

09:02.556 --> 09:03.821
Just as much.

09:03.823 --> 09:05.089
A little more, even.

09:05.091 --> 09:07.858
Oh, uh, only 'cause you
have nothing to do all day.

09:07.860 --> 09:09.427
Are we having
this fight again?

09:09.429 --> 09:11.196
Writing plays is a real job!

09:11.198 --> 09:14.832
I work 90 hours a week
subsidizing your "real job."

09:14.834 --> 09:15.967
I won a Tony!

09:15.969 --> 09:18.336
I brought French cooking
to America!

09:18.338 --> 09:20.104
What?

09:20.106 --> 09:22.941
Let's do shots.
Uh, no, thank you, Barney.

09:22.943 --> 09:25.743
I have that fishing
trip with J.J. early tomorrow.

09:25.745 --> 09:28.179
I-I better take it easy.
No.

09:28.181 --> 09:30.648
Don't you remember what you said
to me when I was a kid?

09:30.650 --> 09:32.984
"Never stop partying."

09:32.986 --> 09:34.485
I said <i>that?</i>

09:34.487 --> 09:36.287
To a six-year-old?

09:36.922 --> 09:37.989
I don't remember that.

09:37.991 --> 09:39.557
You don't remember
the last thing

09:39.559 --> 09:41.960
you said to me when I was a kid?

09:42.895 --> 09:43.995
Well...

09:43.997 --> 09:45.997
you know, why don't you
just go back home?

09:45.999 --> 09:47.615
But I want to hang out with you.

09:47.617 --> 09:49.934
Yeah, well, I want to hang out
with Crazy Jerry,

09:49.936 --> 09:52.270
not Stay-at-Home Jerome.

09:52.272 --> 09:54.439
Fine.

