Oh...

10:23.320 --> 10:26.987
Hey, sugar!
Five beers for the table,

10:27.080 --> 10:28.580
a Seven-and-Seven for me,

10:28.582 --> 10:31.216
and your ten digits
for this guy here!

10:31.218 --> 10:35.437
