10:46.633 --> 10:50.602
I finally know what it's like
to be embarrassed by my dad.

10:51.370 --> 10:52.470
So you really believe

10:52.472 --> 10:54.873
that if we were in
an open marriage

10:54.875 --> 10:57.175
that you would do better than me?
Hey,

10:57.177 --> 10:59.761
you do better than me
at a lot of other things,

10:59.763 --> 11:01.579
like digesting dairy...

11:01.581 --> 11:04.048
and reaching for stuff.

11:04.050 --> 11:05.283
Okay, you know what?

11:05.285 --> 11:06.451
Game on.

11:06.453 --> 11:09.320
If I can score five
numbers before you can,

11:09.322 --> 11:11.589
then we have sex
in the bathroom.

11:11.591 --> 11:12.691
But...

11:12.693 --> 11:15.160
if you can score
five numbers before me,

11:15.162 --> 11:17.729
then we have sex
in the bathroom.

11:17.731 --> 11:18.963
So our usual wager.

11:19.465 --> 11:21.032
Deal.

11:23.285 --> 11:24.669
Hey, uh, hey, Jerry,

11:24.671 --> 11:27.038
y-you really want to be
out here like this?

11:27.040 --> 11:29.090
Oh, sorry, small-town preacher
from the Midwest,

11:29.092 --> 11:32.243
is there a law against dancing?

11:32.245 --> 11:34.095
No, of course not.
I-I just...

11:34.097 --> 11:35.296
Oh, this club blows.

11:35.298 --> 11:37.582
Let's hit the greatest
party in the world,

11:37.584 --> 11:39.350
the streets of New York!

11:39.352 --> 11:41.419
Yeah! Let's do it!
Yeah!

11:41.421 --> 11:44.255
Uh, maybe fix the tie.

11:44.257 --> 11:46.424
But mostly, party!

11:47.977 --> 11:49.644
Okay, Jerry's gone;
let's break up.

11:49.646 --> 11:52.597
Okay. "I would have stolen you
a whole orchestra."

11:52.599 --> 11:54.065
There. What's the rush?

11:54.067 --> 11:56.601
Well, that guy who came over
here who thinks we're dating,

11:56.603 --> 11:58.036
I kind of have
a crush on him.

11:58.038 --> 11:59.270
Can you help me
clear it up?

11:59.272 --> 12:00.772
Really? That guy?

12:00.774 --> 12:02.240
He was, like, a four.

12:02.242 --> 12:06.377
A four? God, you are, like,
the worst judge of guys ever.

12:06.379 --> 12:08.975
Okay, if he is a
four, what are you?

12:08.976 --> 12:09.751
Hey!

12:09.850 --> 12:12.050
I'm not perfect;
I'm an eight...

12:12.052 --> 12:13.918
and a half.

12:13.920 --> 12:15.920
You're a doofus and a half.

12:15.922 --> 12:17.589
Fine. Let's go talk to him.

12:17.591 --> 12:19.424
Where'd you meet
this booger-eater anyway?

12:19.426 --> 12:21.893
At a close-out
sale at Dawes.

12:21.895 --> 12:23.928
Really?
I remember that sale.

12:24.730 --> 12:25.797
Hey, Robin.

12:25.799 --> 12:27.532
Oh, Ted. Oh, no.

12:27.534 --> 12:29.200
