Hold on.
We were dating then.

12:34.841 --> 12:36.207
I specifically remember,

12:36.209 --> 12:38.576
because we had great
sex that night.

12:38.578 --> 12:40.945
Great sex.

12:41.814 --> 12:43.031
Let me guess.

12:43.033 --> 12:44.382
Someone wants to knock...

12:44.384 --> 12:46.851
boots.

12:48.420 --> 12:49.454
Boots.

12:49.456 --> 12:51.523
Just take off your damn shirt.
Okay.

12:51.525 --> 12:52.874
All right.

12:52.876 --> 12:54.592
All right. Whoa,

12:54.594 --> 12:55.844
stop.
What?

12:55.846 --> 12:57.095
Stop. Perfect.

12:57.097 --> 12:59.631
But I-I can't see,
and you can't see me.

12:59.633 --> 13:03.134
Yeah. Yeah, just like that.

13:03.136 --> 13:05.970
You were picturing your crush!
Well,

13:05.972 --> 13:08.039
<i>somebody</i> had to.

13:09.909 --> 13:12.777
Okay, okay, answer me this.

13:12.779 --> 13:16.514
Are you absolutely sure
it had nothing whatsoever...

13:16.516 --> 13:18.850
to do with the boots?

13:18.852 --> 13:20.418
Yes.

13:21.587 --> 13:22.620
You hear that, everybody?

13:22.622 --> 13:25.223
She said "yes"!
We're getting married!

13:26.293 --> 13:27.458
I love this girl.

13:27.460 --> 13:29.127
I'm never letting her go.

13:35.035 --> 13:37.919
Hey... Bottoms up, amigo!

13:37.921 --> 13:39.554
<i>After that,</i>

13:39.556 --> 13:42.173
<i>Barney's memory of the night</i>
<i>got a little hazy.</i>

13:42.175 --> 13:44.008
You want to fight me?

13:44.777 --> 13:48.980
Well, I'll fight you, dummy!

13:48.982 --> 13:51.182
You don't even know!

13:51.184 --> 13:53.017
Hey, hey! There we go!

13:58.791 --> 14:01.192
Oh, look what I just ripped
out of the ground!

14:01.194 --> 14:02.827
Oh...!

14:04.197 --> 14:06.798
I just puked on the
hood of that...

14:06.800 --> 14:09.334
...police car!

14:12.433 --> 14:14.001
Too bad your
playwright friend

14:14.039 --> 14:15.999
isn't a lawyer.

14:20.726 --> 14:22.562
Barney, I'm so sorry.

14:23.503 --> 14:24.870
I'm afraid this
is what it's like

14:24.890 --> 14:27.090
hanging out with
Crazy Jerry.

14:28.158 --> 14:30.692
It's okay, Dad.

14:30.694 --> 14:34.830
I never thought tonight
would be so awesome!

14:34.832 --> 14:36.097
So...

14:36.099 --> 14:37.866
next stop, strip club.

14:37.868 --> 14:39.734
The Lusty Leopard
has a special...

14:39.736 --> 14:42.170
Oh, for corn's sake,
Barney, I'm not drunk!

14:42.172 --> 14:43.572
What?
I told you,

14:43.574 --> 14:44.906
I don't party anymore,

14:44.908 --> 14:47.275
and you wouldn't take
no for an answer.

14:47.277 --> 14:48.343
So...

14:48.345 --> 14:52.180
<i>I used a little...</i>
<i>sleight-of-hand...</i>

14:53.549 --> 14:56.818
...to make you think otherwise.

14:56.820 --> 14:58.170
Here you go.

14:58.172 --> 14:59.988
Whoa!

14:59.990 --> 15:02.190
Bottoms up, amigo!

15:03.677 --> 15:05.093
Mm.

15:05.095 --> 15:07.662
But all those
crazy things you did.

15:07.664 --> 15:11.299
Do you happen to remember what
a magician's best friend is?

15:12.168 --> 15:14.969
A drunk audience.

15:14.971 --> 15:17.539
You want to fight me?

15:17.541 --> 15:20.976
Well, I'll fight you, dummy!

15:20.978 --> 15:22.811
No, no, no.

15:22.813 --> 15:25.814
You don't even know!

15:25.816 --> 15:26.815
Right here!

15:26.817 --> 15:28.350
Look.

15:29.418 --> 15:31.519
Look what I just
ripped out of the ground!

15:31.521 --> 15:32.520
Oh...!

15:36.677 --> 15:38.159
What just happened?

15:38.161 --> 15:40.762
I... I just puked
on the hood of that...

15:42.499 --> 15:43.798
...police car.

15:46.169 --> 15:48.069
Well, why do
all those things?

15:48.071 --> 15:50.272
I figured if I
showed you what...

15:50.274 --> 15:52.774
"never stop partying"
really looked like,

15:52.776 --> 15:55.977
you'd realize you
can't do it forever.

15:56.913 --> 15:59.347
Oh, well.

16:01.083 --> 16:05.954
You lied to me all night
for your own selfish reasons?

16:06.923 --> 16:08.957
Daddy...!

16:10.026 --> 16:13.261
I wanted to hang out
with you-- you're my son.

16:13.263 --> 16:15.764
And since you didn't want
to come with me and J.J.

16:15.766 --> 16:17.165
on that fishing tri--

16:17.167 --> 16:19.935
Fishing trip.

16:19.937 --> 16:23.204
I'll never make it
back in time now.

16:26.042 --> 16:28.677
Hey, you know, a-a pretty
good magician like you

16:28.679 --> 16:30.178
probably knows
how to, say,

16:30.180 --> 16:33.014
get out of a standard
set of handcuffs.

16:33.016 --> 16:35.116
Perhaps.

16:36.319 --> 16:38.987
Well, here's something
you didn't know--

16:38.989 --> 16:41.957
I'm a pretty good
magician, too.

16:45.612 --> 16:47.529
Abracadabra!

16:48.799 --> 16:50.615
Congratulations!

16:50.617 --> 16:52.500
Oh, hey!
Thank you so much.

16:52.502 --> 16:54.836
We're super excited.
We're thinking June.

16:54.838 --> 16:56.271
Yeah, okay.

16:56.273 --> 16:57.806
Okay, jerk...

16:57.808 --> 17:01.309
do you remember how you ended up
buying those red cowboy boots?

17:01.311 --> 17:02.544
Wow.

17:02.546 --> 17:05.512
Wardrobe malfunction
at the O.K. Corral!

17:05.515 --> 17:07.932
I mean, who in their
right mind would ever...

17:07.934 --> 17:10.752
You would look
so totally hot in those.

17:10.753 --> 17:13.087
Do you have these in a size 11?

17:13.990 --> 17:15.991
So get off the field
at the Superdome,

17:15.992 --> 17:17.625
because you ain't no saint.

17:18.560 --> 17:20.362
Hello.

17:20.364 --> 17:21.780
I, uh...
Oh.

17:21.781 --> 17:23.999
Hi, Robin.

17:25.201 --> 17:28.737
Could I have
your phone number?

17:28.739 --> 17:31.206
We need someplace to hide.
Where?

17:31.208 --> 17:33.541
No, Jerry, this is not the time
to go to another club!

17:33.543 --> 17:37.345
We've got to get you back
home in time for that trip.

17:37.347 --> 17:39.848
But there's no more
trains, there's no cabs.

17:39.850 --> 17:41.016
Well, uh...

17:41.018 --> 17:44.636
I do have a few driving
students in the city.

17:44.638 --> 17:46.588
Step on it! Jerry...
Do not step on it.

17:46.590 --> 17:48.189
Jerry, we have got
to get you home

17:48.191 --> 17:49.424
in time for
that fishing trip.

17:49.426 --> 17:50.725
...the laws are there
to protect...

17:50.727 --> 17:52.344
This is no time for laws!
Buckle up, Barney.

17:52.346 --> 17:55.847
I am not going to buckle up!
I am your father! You will listen to me!

17:58.934 --> 18:01.436
Hey! How's the
open marriage going?

18:01.438 --> 18:03.138
Who was the first one
to get the five numbers?

18:03.140 --> 18:04.239
I won that race.

18:04.241 --> 18:06.875
My prize--
sex in the bathroom.

18:06.877 --> 18:09.611
And I won <i>that</i> race.

18:12.782 --> 18:15.116
Aw, sorry that secret crush
didn't work out for you.

18:15.118 --> 18:19.287
Oh, it's okay. I guess
it just wasn't meant to be.

18:19.289 --> 18:20.822
Why are you smiling?

18:20.824 --> 18:22.223
I don't know.

18:22.225 --> 18:24.659
Good night.

18:24.661 --> 18:26.461
Saw that girl again.

18:26.463 --> 18:28.596
And guess what?
She's engaged.

18:28.598 --> 18:30.131
So that's the end of that.

18:30.133 --> 18:32.550
<i>It wasn't the end of that.</i>
<i>More on that later.</i>

18:32.552 --> 18:36.471
And her fiancé?
The guy's like a two.

18:39.208 --> 18:41.509
How did you do it?

18:41.511 --> 18:43.010
Do what?

18:43.012 --> 18:45.346
How did you become this?

18:45.348 --> 18:48.283
I mean, I love my life, but...

18:48.285 --> 18:51.619
I'm not sure I <i>like</i>
loving it.

18:51.621 --> 18:54.322
Sure, strip clubs...
You're drifting.

18:54.324 --> 18:56.091
Hey, I'm trying to
open up to you...

18:56.093 --> 18:58.793
No, Mrs. Perkins,
you're drifting!

18:59.662 --> 19:02.197
Go on, Barney.

19:02.199 --> 19:06.134
When I think about going for
anything more than that,

19:06.136 --> 19:11.239
I look at my life,
and who I am, and...

19:11.241 --> 19:15.076
I'm too far gone.

19:15.078 --> 19:17.212
I'm broken.

19:19.181 --> 19:23.568
Son, I was far more broken
than you'll ever be.

19:23.570 --> 19:26.053
And look at me now.

19:26.055 --> 19:31.192
Don't get me wrong-- settling
down is... a challenge.

19:31.194 --> 19:33.461
It's the biggest
challenge of your life.

19:33.463 --> 19:35.263
So how do you do it?

19:35.265 --> 19:39.300
A magician never reveals
his greatest trick.

19:40.236 --> 19:42.103
But I'll give you a hint.

19:42.105 --> 19:44.739
You gotta meet the right girl.

19:46.108 --> 19:48.626
Who knows?

19:48.628 --> 19:51.412
Maybe you'll meet her tomorrow.

19:51.414 --> 19:54.883
Maybe I've met her already.

19:55.985 --> 19:58.803
And park.
And emergency brake.

20:00.990 --> 20:02.724
I did have a good time tonight.

20:02.726 --> 20:04.125
And hey,
if you want to

20:04.127 --> 20:06.094
go fishing,
we got room in the boat.

20:06.096 --> 20:08.596
Maybe some other time.

20:08.598 --> 20:09.964
Okay.

20:11.066 --> 20:12.400
Oh, and, uh...

20:12.402 --> 20:16.604
thanks for taking such
good care of this.

20:16.606 --> 20:20.074
It means a lot to me that you
kept it safe all these years.

20:36.492 --> 20:38.960
I'm going fishing with my dad.

20:57.993 --> 21:01.362
This...

21:01.364 --> 21:03.197
